snippet.textDisplay: Can anyone from my Pakistani Brothers please tell me about the native place of my family....Zulfikaar Chachaji, lovingly remembered by us all, were the Pagg-Watt bhra of my father,they were class fellows and were Partners in the Aarhat Shop... Zulfikaar Chachaji de bahut Ahasaan ne saadi Family utte ..... I just want to know about his family. Shaala ohna da khandaan jug jug jeeve.... Kaash i can visit our village in Pakistan.... WaaheGuru shayad kde mehar kar deve..... Both our countries have Mohabbat,Khaloos and Brotherhood for each other. Best Wishes to all my brothers and sisters from Satluj Paar.... I love you all..

snippet.textDisplay: I am from Muktsar, Punjab... before Partition our village was Chakk No-9,Chishatian Mandi,Bahawalpur....Bholewali Mandi... my Grand Parents longed to visit their Native Place... my Father was studying in Law College, Lahore....all have gone now. My both Sisters and my elder Brother are born in Pakistan.... Nobody can forget their birth place....
